    dc:title "Description of the Immature Stages and Redescription of the Adults of Ancognatha scarabaeoides Erichson (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae: Dynastinae), A Member of the Soil White Grub Assemblage in Colombia" ;
    bibo:endPage "164" ;
