<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111139>
    dc:description "Figs. 1–7. Ancognatha scarabaeoides. Adult. 1) male head and pronotum; 2) male antenna; 3) male fore leg; 4) female fore tarsal claws; 5) male genital capsule, distal view; 6) same, latero-ventral view; 7) same, ventral view. Scale lines 5 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111139/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111141>
    dc:description "Figs. 8–13. Ancognatha scarabaeoides. Third instar larva. 8) head, frontal view; 9) epipharynx; 10) left mandible, dorsal view; 11) right mandible, dorsal view; 12) right mandible, ventral view; 13) left mandible, ventral view. Scale lines 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111141/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111143>
    dc:description "Figs. 14–20. Ancognatha scarabaeoides. Third instar larva. 14) right maxilla, dorsal view; 15) left maxilla and hypopharynx, dorsal view; 16) antenna, lateral view; 17) apex of hind leg, lateral view; 18) raster; 19) detail of respiratory plate; 20) abdominal spiracle. Scale lines: Figs. 14–17 5 1 mm; Fig. 18 5 10 mm; Fig. 19 5 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111143/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111145>
    dc:description "Figs. 21–23. Ancognatha scarabaeoides. Female pupa. 21) dorsal view; 22) ventral view;" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111145/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

